    "body": ":+1: understood. Now we have a pretty good idea of what we need to do. If we do not plan to do this right now but later on, then I would wrap it up in a complete proposal: changes to be made on which widgets, which connectors, new exposed props, new provided props).\r\n\r\nAn action plan so that when we get back to this in two weeks we know exactly what to do. What do you think?",
